Ensure all text files use LF line endings





text=auto eol=lf

Explicitly set LF for specific file types

*.py text eol=lf *.js text eol=lf *.ts text eol=lf *.json text eol=lf *.md text eol=lf *.yml text eol=lf *.yaml text eol=lf *.sh text eol=lf *.txt text eol=lf

Windows-specific files that should keep CRLF

*.bat text eol=crlf *.ps1 text eol=crlf